# papers/ holds source PDFs and supplements (copyrighted publisher
# content -- never commit), alongside per-paper verification.md notes
# that document our line-by-line audit of each paper against the
# package code. Exclude the publisher content; keep the verification
# notes under version control.
papers/**/*.pdf
papers/**/*.xls
papers/**/*.xlsx
papers/**/*.xlsm
papers/**/*.csv

# Scratch outputs from verification scripts under notes/. The .R
# scripts are version-controlled (reproducible); their .out dumps are
# regeneratable and bulky.
notes/*.out
/doc/
/Meta/

# covr local coverage reports
covr-report.html
/lib/
Rplots.pdf
